        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4" style="line-height: 1.2; color: #260d5e;">
          What to Do If Someone Has a Seizure While Waiting for a Doctor
        </h1>
        <!-- Brief problem description -->
        <p class="lead text-muted">
          Seizures require prompt, careful action to protect the individual until medical help arrives.
        </p>
        <!-- Short symptoms section in red -->
        <p class="fs-5" style="color: red;">
          <strong>Symptoms:</strong> Uncontrolled shaking, loss of awareness, and confusion.
        </p>
      </div>
